Roku-DVP-Remote version 0.01
============================

Use this module to interface with a Roku device. Included is an XUL
GUI example program which provides a neat Roku remote that you can
run on your computer.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   URI
   Readonly
   IO::Socket::INET
   Net::Ifconfig::Wrapper
   Net::Ping

For the example/remote.pl program:

   Env
   XUL::Gui

